{
  "stem": "23131.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, they got rid of the people that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --of the people that they knew from-- that wanted to take on them, you know-- to pay them off for what they did.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Tovia's brothers, for the Russian, they were some kind of-- it was in the-- in the little village, they managed-- they-- something-- were involved in the communist party or-- and in the management or whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so after, when the Germans came, they wanted to pay them off for it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were looking for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They only wanted to get rid of the Bielskys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But some of them favored them, because my husband did quite a few good things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He saved one person's life when he was drowning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his father and the son could not forget that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then-- and-- and he had very good friends in the army, when he was in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those are people that he was one of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His languages were so pure and he is so good, that nobody could even find out that he's a Jew in that time-- not by looks, and not by-- by speech.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So some of them tried to bury them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them tried to save them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they knew the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They grew up with those people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they knew them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And slowly, slowly, first he started with the Nowogrodek ghetto, and then he started with the Lida ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was carrying on terribly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember he was asked just recently, what would you like-- to kill 10 Germans or to save 1 Jew?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his answer was always, I want to save 1 Jew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was his main aim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's-- nobody came.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
